<!-- Story Section -->
<section class="bg-secondary/30 py-16">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center gradient-text">Our Story</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                    VeriXSoft was founded in 2019 by a group of passionate software engineers and entrepreneurs 
                    who saw a gap in the market for high-quality, personalized software solutions. What started as a small team 
                    of five developers has grown into a dynamic organization of over 50 talented professionals.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Our first project was a web application for a local e-commerce startup. Despite the challenges, 
                    we delivered an innovative solution that exceeded expectations. That success became the foundation of VeriXSoft.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Today, we're proud to have worked with startups, SMEs, and enterprise clients across various industries 
                    including fintech, healthcare, e-commerce, and education. Our portfolio includes over 50 successful projects 
                    with a 100% client satisfaction rate.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

